  2004-09-23 21:49:44 by rcaputo; mylib/ExtUtils/AutoInstall.pm 1.6

    17:35 <autrijus> dngor: hey. you may wish to start shipping POE with
    EU::AI 0.60 soonish. CPANPLUS 0.050 and later had a problem with
